    <h2>Drivers Privacy Protection Act (DPPA) Permissible Use Descriptions</h2>
    <p>
        Below is a more detailed description of the DPPA permissible uses. Each description
        is followed by a list of states that recognize the permissible use. By selecting a
        permissible use, your search will be run against the drivers' licenses, motor vehicle
        registrations and boat registrations for the states that recognize the permissible use
        you selected. If you select I Do Not Have a Permissible Use, your search results will
        not include drivers' licenses, motor vehicle registrations and boat registrations.
    </p>
    <h3>I have no Permissible Use (Searches Unregulated Data Only)</h3>
    <p>For persons who do not have a DPPA permissible use.</p>
    <h3>Litigation</h3>
    <p>Use in connection with any proceeding (including arbitration) in any court or government agency, or before any self-regulatory body, including investigation in anticipation of litigation</p>
    <p><strong>Boat Registrations:</strong> Permitted by USCG, AK, AL, AR, AZ, CO, GA, IL, IA, KY, KS, ME, MI, MN, MS, MT, NC, ND, NE, NV, NY, OH, SC, TN, TX, UT, VA, WI, WV, WY</p>
    <p><strong>Drivers Licenses:</strong> Permitted by CO, DE, ID, IL, KY, ME, MI, MN, MS, ND, NE, NV, OH, SC, TN, TX, WI</p>
    <p><strong>Motor Vehicle Registrations:</strong> Depending on the search terms submitted, permissible states may include AK, AL, CO, CT, DC, DE, FL, GA, IA, ID, IL, KY, LA, MD, ME, MI, MN, MO, MS, MT, NC, ND, NE, NJ, NV, NY, OH, PR, RI, SC, SD, TN, TX, UT, VT, WI, WV, WY</p>
    <h3>Debt Recovery/Fraud</h3>
    <p>Use to verify the accuracy of information about a person who provided the information to you (or to your client) but only if used to recover on a debt against the person or to pursue legal remedies against the person for fraud.</p>
    <p><strong>Boat Registrations:</strong> Permitted by USCG, AK, AL, AR, AZ, CO, FL, GA, IL, IA, KY, KS, MA, ME, MI, MN, MS, MT, NC, ND, NE, NY, OH, SC, TN, TX, UT, VA, WI, WV, WY</p>
    <p><strong>Drivers Licenses:</strong> Permitted by CO, DE, FL, ID, IL, KY, MA, ME, MI, MN, MS, ND, NE, NV, OH, SC, TN, TX, WI, WV</p>
    <p><strong>Motor Vehicle Registrations:</strong> Depending on the search terms submitted, permissible states may include AK, AL, CO, DC, DE, FL, GA, IA, ID, IL, IN, KY, LA, MA, MD, ME, MI, MN, MO, MS, MT, NC, ND, NE, NJ, NY, OH, PR, RI, SC, SD, TN, TX, UT, VT, WI, WV, WY</p>
    <h3>Government Agency</h3>
    <p>Use by a government agency but only in carrying out its functions.</p>
    <p><strong>Boat Registrations:</strong> Permitted by USCG, AK, AL, AR, AZ, CO, CT, FL, GA, IL, IA, KY, KS, MD, ME, MI, MN, MS, MT, NC, ND, NE, NV, NY, OH, SC, TN, TX, UT, VA, WI, WV, WY</p>
    <p><strong>Drivers Licenses:</strong> Permitted by CO, DE, FL, ID, IL, KY, MD, ME, MI, MN, MS, ND, NE, NV, OH, SC, TN, TX, WI, WV</p>
    <p><strong>Motor Vehicle Registrations:</strong> Depending on the search terms submitted, permissible states may include AK, AL, AZ, CO, CT, DC, DE, FL, GA, IA, ID, IL, IN, KS, KY, LA, MA, MD, ME, MI, MN, MO, MS, MT, NC, ND, NE, NJ, NM, NV, NY, OH, OK, PR, RI, SC, SD, TN, TX, UT, VT, WI, WV, WY</p>
    <h3>On Government Behalf</h3>
    <p>Use by any person acting on behalf of a government agency but only in carrying out the agency.s functions.</p>
    <p><strong>Boat Registrations:</strong> Permitted by USCG, AK, AL, AR, AZ, CO, CT, FL, GA, IL, IA, KY, KS, ME, MI, MN, MS, MT, NC, ND, NE, NV, NY, OH, SC, TN, TX, UT, VA, WI, WV, WY</p>
