    <p>Use by an insurer (or its agent) in connection with claims investigation activities, antifraud activities, rating or underwriting.</p>
    <p><strong>Boat Registrations:</strong> Permitted by USCG, AK, AL, AR, AZ, CO, CT, FL, GA, IL, IA, KY, KS, MD, ME, MI, MN, MO, MS, MT, NC, ND, NE, NV, NY, OH, SC, TN, TX, UT, VA, WI, WV, WY</p>
